quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  34,32,"Townitinoo…ďe …ďenmbi'ani lo'inanoo…ďe …ďen: "E ko minen palinoo on e peewal …ďaawo ngal arde e mon? Si ko woni, on ngoniino bon…ďe"."
  34,33,"Lo'inanoo…ďe …ďen kadi mbi'ani townitinoo…ďe …ďen: "Si ko woni, ko pewje (mon) jemma e √Īalawma, tuma njamirayno…óon meon yo men njeddu Alla, min mba…óana Mo potondir…ói". ∆Āe cuu…ói nimse …óen, nde …ďe njinoo lepte …óen. Min mba…ói kolombooje e daa…óe …ďen yeddu…ďe. Hara …ďe yo…ďitete si wanaa ko …ďe ngollatnoo oo kon?"
  34,34,"Min Nulaani jeertinoowo e yim…ďe saare, si wanaa neeminaa…ďe mayre …ďen mbiay: "Minen ko men yeddu…ďe ko nulida…óon kon"."
  34,35,"∆Āe mbi'i kadi: "Ko menen …ďuri …óuu…óude jaw…óe e …ďi…ď…ďe, men wonaani kadi leptetee…ďe"."
  34,36,"Maaku: "pellet, Joomi am homo weertana arsike on, mo O muuyi, O …ďillini (mo O muuyi). Kono …ďur…ďe …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen, …ďe nganndaa"."
  34,37,"Wonaa jaw…óe mon, wonaa jiidi mon woni ko …ďa…ótinirta on ka Amen …ďadal. Si wonaa …ďen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe; …ďen …óon, hino woodani …ďe njo…ďdi sowaande, sabu ko …ďe ngolli kon, kam…ďe ka soorooji, ko …ďe hoolii…ďe."
  34,38,"∆Āeen yaccotoo…ďe e doŇčkingol (yim…ďe …ďeen) e Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ďen …óon, ka ka ndeer lepte woni ko …ďe tawnoytee."
  34,39,"Maaku: "pellet, Joomi am homo weertana arsike on, mo o muuyani e jeyaa…ďe makko …ďen, O …ďillini mo (O muuyi e ma…ď…ďe). Kala non ko winti…óon e hu'unde, KaŇčko O lomtinay nde. Ko KaŇčko woni mo∆ī∆īo Arsikoowo"."